data.description: Price Reduced!!! New Roof, New 4 Ton AC &  New Pool Heater. Take a look at this one!! 4 Bedroom + Den, 3 Bath, 2536 Sq. Ft of Living Plus 3 Car Garage and a Nice Lanai with Pool all located on a Corner Lot just off Rose Garden Rd, on your way to Tarpon Point. Rotary Park entrances are just steps away. This home offers all Tile Flooring, a Large Master Bedroom connected to a Master Bath with separate Tub & Shower. 3 Bedrooms located on the other side of the house makes this your own Private Retreat. All bedrooms are good sized with plenty of room. Family and Living Room both offer plenty of space for relaxing or entertaining. The Den is large enough for a Murphy Bed to give you Lots of extra bed space. Sliders from the living area, master bedroom, dining room and a pass through window from the kitchen to Lanai making it easy for family & guests. Granite Counters throughout Kitchen and Baths. Under Truss Lanai gives you a plenty of shade to enjoy along with the good sized pool. The 3 Car Garage has plenty of room for your Autos as well as your Toys. Not far from Tarpon Point, Dining and Entertainment. This home and Location would be Perfect for the growing family or Vacation Rental.
